casebody.data:
Thursday, February 1, 1996

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

95-2098. Jefferson Cty. Dept. of Human Serv. v. Communication Workers of Am., Local 4527.

Jefferson County, No. 93-J-49. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted, effective January 31,1996.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
